title: S2 Episode 18: The One About Haters
description:
This week Bob and Miz Cracker invite special guest Honey Davenport to talk about haters and what it's like to be on the set of RuPaul's Drag Race. Cracker challenges Bob to read online hate to each other to guess which hate is fake and which is real. Want to see the full episodes first? Head over to https://www.patreon.com/siblingrivalrypodcast to be the first to see our latest Sibling Rivalry Podcast Videos + extended cuts!
